nodes.statement_display:
Let \(\varphi\) be a sentence and let \(\mathcal M\) be a structure for the
language of \(\varphi\). The structure \(\mathcal M\) is a \emph{model of}
\(\varphi\) exactly when \(\mathcal M\models\varphi\).

