nodes.statement_display:
The propositional formula constructors are injective:
\begin{enumerate}
\item if \(\neg\varphi=\neg\psi\), then \(\varphi=\psi\);
\item if \((\varphi\circ\psi)=(\alpha\star\beta)\), then \(\varphi=\alpha\), \(\psi=\beta\), and \(\circ=\star\).
\end{enumerate}

