nodes.statement_display:
For any binary relation $R$ on $X$, define:
\begin{itemize}
  \item the \emph{symmetric part}: $xIy \iff xRy \text{ and } yRx$
  \item the \emph{asymmetric part}: $xPy \iff xRy \text{ but not } yRx$
\end{itemize}
Note that $R = P \cup I$.

